Package com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude

Class DefaultSolicitude.Context

java.lang.Object
com.sicomsa.dmt.solicitude.DefaultSolicitude.Context
All Implemented Interfaces:
DownloadContext
Enclosing class:
DefaultSolicitude
protected class DefaultSolicitude.Context extends Object implements DownloadContext
Concrete implementation of DownloadContext.

Basically forwards its methods to solicitude's instance methods.

Download context was decided to be implemented through this subclass instead of in DefaultSolicitude for protecting to a certain point solicitude's consistency
